title: Starship ready for maiden launch attempt
summary: The world’s most powerful rocket in history is set to make its first launch attempt on Monday, the first major step to making life multi-planetary. Liftoff of Starship from Starbase, Texas is set to occur within a 2.5-hour window that opens at 07:00 CDT. Wind shear is the only watch item as a potential constraint.
